`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Shieldcharge
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * shield charge <victim>

 This skill, which can only be used by legionnaires and knights, allows the 
user to slam into the victim with his or her shield, knocking the victim  off
its feet and causing damage in the process.

